  "summary": "Important: skopeo security update",
  "details": "The skopeo command lets you inspect images from container image registries, get images and image layers, and use signatures to create and verify files.   \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * encoding/gob: golang: Calling Decoder.Decode on a message which contains deeply nested structures can cause a panic due to stack exhaustion (CVE-2024-34156)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
